        correct: 2,
        rationale: "Normal EEG alpha rhythm confirms intact cortical function, and appropriate eye movement responses to commands demonstrate preserved consciousness and cognition. This differentiates LIS from vegetative state (which shows variable EEG without purposeful responses) and coma (which shows diffuse EEG slowing without arousal)."
